@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@staffRole = STAFF

### Product search by text query (STAFF+)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/search?q=tube&take=20&skip=0
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: demo-staff

### Product search by barcode (STAFF+)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/search?barcode=1234567890123&take=20&skip=0
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: demo-staff

